defaultQ23 default&#xa0; 
defaultMr Walker:default Mr Hargreaves, you mentioned the potential for major projects like York potash, which obviously has substantial potential but has been quite a long time in the offing, to put it mildly.  Do you feel that that is in any way a victim of the intensity of the regulatory regime
