defaultQ24 default&#xa0; 
defaultMr Binley:default Can I relate what you have just said to the aggregates extraction industry?  It seems to me that that is a very finite resource that is quickly coming to an end.  I wonder whether there is a way of linking extraction more firmly with recycling in respect of the aggregates extraction industry.
